data.description: Welcome Home! This 4 bed/2bath home has been meticulous cared for & is ready for its new owner. Spacious living throughout. Kitchen is beautiful and bright, spacious cabinetry, new counters and plenty of room for more than 1 cook in the kitchen. Family room off the kitchen has many uses.  Bedrooms are generously sized. Primary bed has a walk-in closet.  Both bathrooms have been modernized with decorative tile showers, newer fixtures and cabinetry. Relax under the full length covered back patio, block walls for extra privacy, with many outside seating areas and a wonderful fireplace to enjoy the outdoors. Pavers & gravel help with the low-maintenance backyard. Don't miss this house, it has everything you've been looking for!
